Saudi Arabia ’s Capital Market
Authority plans to raise the level of disclosure and
transparency by companies trading on the kingdom’s bourse,  Arab
News  reported, citing Chairman Abdulrahman al-Tuwaijri.  To contact the reporter on this story:
